Here local host is my local machine that is my currect laptop .

C:\Users\Ilakkiya R>nslookup localhost
Server:  UnKnown
Address:  192.168.43.1

Name:    localhost
Addresses:  ::1
          127.0.0.1

::1 is for IPv6 
127.0.0.1 for IPv4


this is the host file located on our machine includes mappings of hostnames to ip address - C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts .
The traffic sent either to 127.0.0.1 or ::1 is looped back to the own computer network interface .

localhost:8080/demo/

localhost -> indicates that appln is running on your local machine .
8080 -> port number on which your web server (Apache tomcat) is listening to the connections .
/DemoApp ->Name of the project deployed on the server 
